text: The Transylvanian Carpathians may refer to: * Eastern Transylvanian Carpathians, a designation for the Eastern Romanian Carpathians * Southern Transylvanian Carpathians, a designation for the Southern Romanian Carpathians * Western Transylvanian Carpathians, a designation for the Western Romanian Carpathians ==See also== * Romanian Carpathians * Carpathian Mountains * Carpathian (disambiguation) * Transylvania (disambiguation) * Transylvanian (disambiguation)
title: Transylvanian Carpathians
